snippet.title: Unioverse Proving Grounds - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Test Your Skills in Our Proving Grounds, Launching April 26th! Built as a mode in our Unioverse Viewer, the Proving Grounds lets you play your Reyu Hero in an actual game environment. Drop the same Reyu you have in your wallet into the Proving Grounds and jump, shoot, and wall-run your way through the course.

Install here: https://launcher.elixir.app/browse/the-unioverse-proving-grounds#overview
